


1. NODE

https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/how-to-install-node-js-on-ubuntu-20-04-de



2. GET CODE

sudo adduser --disabled-password --disabled-login exomag
sudo -i -u exomag
cd /home/exomag
git -c http.sslVerify=false clone https://git.meb.uni-bonn.de/aschmid/exom-ag-database.git



3. INSTALL

cd exomag
npm install

cd frontend
npm install --legacy-peer-deps



3. CREATE DATABASE STRUCTURE

cd backend
knex migrate:latest



4. SEED TEST DATA

cd backend
./run_base_seed.sh











